\f1\i \outl0\strokewidth-182 paramount. 
\f2\i0 \outl0\strokewidth-182 To that end the amount of tutorialization\'97or any other sort of obstacle between the player and the game itself\'97should be minimized or eliminated entirely.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \ul \outl0\strokewidth-182 \
Radically Simplified Design\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\partightenfactor0
